acceptOwnership().details: The new owner accepts the ownership transfer.

params._amount: The number of uShare tokens to purchase.

buyuShareOnPreSale(bytes32,uint256).details: The user must have at least `minUranoAmountForPreSale` staked to participate.

params._amount: The number of uShare tokens to purchase.

claimRedistribution(bytes32,uint256).details: Closes the redistribution if all uShare tokens have been burned.

params._amountOfShares: The number of uShare tokens the caller wishes to burn.

closeuShareSaleAndWithdrawUsdc(bytes32).details: Only the contract owner can call this. Marks the uShare sale as ended.

params._usdc: Address of the USDC token contract.

createRedistribution(bytes32,uint256).details: Only callable by the owner and only after the uShare sale has ended.

params._amountOfUSDCProfits: The total USDC amount to be distributed as profits.

createuShareSale(address,uint256,uint256.details: Only callable by the uShareFactory contract.

params._minUranoAmountForPreSale: The minimum URANO tokens required to participate in the pre-sale.
params._saleDuration: The duration of the uShare sale in seconds.
params._uShareAmount: The total amount of uShare tokens allocated for the sale.
params._uSharePriceInUSDC: The price of the uShare in USDC (scaled by USHARE_DECIMAL_PRECISION).
params._uShareToken: The address of the newly created uShare token.

params._uShareId: The identifier of the uShare sale.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pendingOwner().details: Returns the address of the pending owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Starts the ownership transfer of the contract to a new account. Replaces the pending transfer if there is one. Can only be called by the current owner. Setting `newOwner` to the zero address is allowed; this can be used to cancel an initiated ownership transfer.

PRE_SALE_DURATION().notice: Two days, used to define the pre-sale duration.

USHARE_DECIMAL_PRECISION().notice: 1e18, used for price calculations with USDC decimals.

buyuShare(bytes32,uint256).notice: Allows anyone to purchase uShare tokens in the public sale phase (after the pre-sale duration ends).

buyuShareOnPreSale(bytes32,uint256).notice: Allows users with the required URANO staking amount to purchase uShare tokens during the pre-sale.

claimRedistribution(bytes32,uint256).notice: Allows uShare token holders to burn their tokens in exchange for a share of the USDC profits.

closeuShareSaleAndWithdrawUsdc(bytes32).notice: Closes the uShare sale after the sale duration has passed, burns any unsold uShare tokens, and withdraws USDC.

constructor.notice: Constructor sets the uShareFactory, token references, and ownership.

createRedistribution(bytes32,uint256).notice: Starts the redistribution of USDC profits among uShare token holders.

createuShareSale(address,uint256,uint256.notice: Creates and initiates a new uShare sale.

getuShareInfo(bytes32).notice: Returns the uShare information for a given uShare ID.

i_minuShareAmountForOneUSDC().notice: Minimum uShare tokens needed to correspond to 1 USDC worth of uShare purchase.

i_staking().notice: Reference to the Staking contract for URANO staking checks.

i_uShareFactory().notice: The uShareFactory that deployed this uShareMarket.

i_uranoToken().notice: Reference to the URANO token contract.

i_usdc().notice: The USDC contract address used for payments and distributions.

i_usdcDecimals().notice: Number of decimals used by the USDC contract.
